tool_description: Convert PDF files to JSON, CSV, EXCEL and Image Files

api_list.name: PDF File to Image
api_list.description:
POST PDF file
if PDF file has 1 image Return Image file (jpg) 
else Returns Zip folder containing all images in the PDF file
(PDF File Must be image based, or has images in it)

api_list.description:

api_list.name: PDF File to EXCEL File
api_list.description:

(PDF File Must be text based)

api_list.name: PDF File to CSV String
api_list.description:
POST PDF file Return CSV string
(PDF File Must be text based)

api_list.name: PDF File to JSON File
api_list.description:
POST PDF file Return JSON File

POST PDF file Return JSON string
